OL,3,C'We're at full capacity': Patients
OL,4,Cqueuing in corridors at hospital
OL,6,FOne of the South West's biggest
OL,7,Fhospitals - with beds for up to 900
OL,8,Fpatients - is operating at "full
OL,9,Fcapacity".
OL,11,FSome patients have been waiting in
OL,12,Fcorridors at Bristol's Southmead
OL,13,FHospital as staff struggle to cope
OL,14,Fwith demand.
OL,16,FAdmissions for flu, Covid and other
OL,17,Fseasonal illnesses have spiked in
OL,18,Frecent weeks, with hospital bosses now
OL,19,Fasking people to wear face masks on
OL,20,Fcertain wards.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@IO]
