OL,3,C'We're at full capacity': Patients
OL,4,Cqueuing in corridors at hospital
OL,6,FProfessor Steve Hams, who is the Chief
OL,7,FNursing Officer for North Bristol NHS
OL,8,FTrust, said they are effectively
OL,9,Foperating a "one patient out, one
OL,10,Fpatient in" policy.
OL,12,F"We're at full capacity here at
OL,13,FSouthmead," he told ITV News West
OL,14,FCountry.
OL,16,F"We do our best to ensure we balance
OL,17,Fthat the best we can. Of course we
OL,18,Fwant to ensure all patients that come
OL,19,Fto us are treated brilliantly and with
OL,20,Freal care and attention but it's a bit
OL,21,Fof a challenge.
OL,26,@qD@MOUrD@KO]tD@AOUuD@KO]xD@AOU
