OL,3,C'We're at full capacity': Patients
OL,4,Cqueuing in corridors at hospital
OL,6,F"We've seen a doubling of the flu
OL,7,Fcases over the last week or so, and we
OL,8,Fexpect that to probably peak in the
OL,9,Fnext couple of weeks.
OL,11,F"Frequently, we do have more patients
OL,12,Fthan we have beds. We can guarantee
OL,13,Fthat if you are poorly and done well,
OL,14,Fwe will always see you...but sometimes
OL,15,Fthat can take a little bit of extra
OL,16,Ftime and regretfully, we do have some
OL,17,Fpatients that do queue in our
OL,18,Fcorridors."
