OL,3,C'We're at full capacity': Patients
OL,4,Cqueuing in corridors at hospital
OL,6,F"The other thing we would say is we've
OL,7,Fintroduced a couple of other control
OL,8,Fmeasures to reduce the spread of
OL,9,Finfections.
OL,11,F"So in our emergency zone, we have
OL,12,Fintroduced mask wearing temporarily so
OL,13,Fthat we can reduce the spread of
OL,14,Finfection.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
