OL,3,C'We're at full capacity': Patients
OL,4,Cqueuing in corridors at hospital
OL,6,F"But we'd also say to families, if you
OL,7,Fhave a loved one in hospital and you
OL,8,Fare feeling unwell, please - if you
OL,9,Fcan - don't come whilst you've got
OL,10,Factive flu or cold symptoms or you may
OL,11,Fhave diarrhoea and vomiting because it
OL,12,Fspreads those infections to very, very
OL,13,Fvulnerable patients."
